{"tid":917261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「我巨乳我驕傲」　她大方露奶不怕恥笑","createTime":"2018-11-26T09:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T11:23:17.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2abb1265c0a206c3c49f1337f105698bc86c0df9","tid":917261,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:52:49.000Z","msg":"澳洲一名女子珍娜(Jana)願意做自己，她大方在公眾場合露奶就算被別人恥笑也絕不退縮，她直呼：「我巨乳我驕傲！」<br />\n <br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，珍娜說，她的阿姨死於乳癌，媽媽也和乳癌病魔對抗「因此我想要展現我身上的資產，因為我不可能永遠擁有這份資產」。珍娜所謂的「資產」，就是她的巨乳，她說：「自己的身體，由自己的規則掌握。」珍娜在公共場合，經常穿著爆乳或露奶裝，大膽展現女性之美，但也常常引來其他人的批評。<br />\n不過珍娜形容這種感覺，就像女生會花時間弄頭髮、化妝<br />\n或者是買了貴霜霜的香水，或許在掏出信用卡的那一刻會心疼，但會讓自己心情好、心情爽，有何不可。<br />\n <br />\n珍娜承認，巨乳常常會被別人視為眼中釘及攻擊的對象<br />\n就像她在職場一樣，曾經被同事騷擾。珍娜說，多年前她曾被同事騷擾，同事故意問她：「可以秀出你度假的照片嗎？不要那種只拍風景照的唷，要那種有奶子的，像泳池旁比基尼照之類的。」珍娜說，這時的她就在想是要笑笑略過，還是把同事拖出去，跟他要一個道歉？最後珍娜選擇前者。<br />\n <br />\n珍娜也說，巨乳的穿衣哲學其實是不容易的，穿太鬆，就會讓胸部鬆跨跨，讓自己的身軀顯得更肥大。但如果穿得很緊身，就會呈現出細腰巨乳的體型，並出現一種獻媚的感覺，她說：「所以我們就要把自己隱藏起來嗎？當然不要！無論你是什麼罩杯，不管你是什麼尺寸，我的奶我驕傲，做你想做的事。」"},{"pid":"abf995852b062c83624c5de81c067c069108acf7","tid":917261,"uid":30063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:53:28.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"33cb124850c3c29b6adfed0bbb076f514b7a1c98","tid":917261,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:53:40.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"e38f49cfd05e09ada768ee12ebb49f808fa70e96","tid":917261,"uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/175503_6a84e8896dd4b6f04b0c4dfddf550578.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F175503_6a84e8896dd4b6f04b0c4dfddf550578.png&h=0accfa48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69605a6c0646489c01b367a9760146d3feefa9da","tid":917261,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:56:12.000Z","msg":"似假"},{"pid":"fd08659747a128d55de92c8c8a83a9410a579a62","tid":917261,"uid":122134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e38f49cfd05e09ada768ee12ebb49f808fa70e96","tid":917261,"uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/175503_6a84e8896dd4b6f04b0c4dfddf550578.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F175503_6a84e8896dd4b6f04b0c4dfddf550578.png&h=0accfa48&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:56:49.000Z","msg":"都唔係好巨姐<br />\n呢D size岩岩好"},{"pid":"5a7a60f9af4e67ec54202f5720f119274186dca3","tid":917261,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁樣叫公開露乳?有咩新聞價值?<br />\n有著衫既喂?"},{"pid":"09dd772e64e861cbd2efb232fe89ae177d97c92d","tid":917261,"uid":55659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680b727d2d00ac6df3838c0473b2f7020df46443","tid":917261,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"胸大先會咁講<br />\n如果佢平板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06633f7d590052c7682c0faaea4e83340a2f35ac","tid":917261,"uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:23:17.000Z","msg":"咁叫巨乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.cyegushi.com/uploads/allimg/160513/1-160513125054-52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.c